### Water Log API Test File
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### 2. Login to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "watertest@gmail.com",
  "password": "adwawdasd"
}

### 3. Create Water Log (replace {{jwt_token}} with actual token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "amount_ml": 250,
  "drink_type": "water",
  "notes": "Morning water"
}

### 4. Create Water Log with specific time
POST http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "amount_ml": 500,
  "drink_type": "water",
  "consumed_at": "2025-09-09T10:30:00Z",
  "notes": "After workout"
}

### 5. Get All Water Logs
GET http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 6. Get Daily Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/stats/daily?date=2025-09-09
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 7. Get Weekly Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/stats/weekly?start_date=2025-09-03&end_date=2025-09-09
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 8. Get Today's Progress
GET http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/progress/today
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 9. Set Daily Water Goal
POST http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/goals/daily
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "daily_goal_ml": 2500
}

### 10. Get Daily Water Goal
GET http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/goals/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 11. Get Water Consumption Trends
GET http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/trends/consumption?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 12. Get Hydration Insights
GET http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/insights/hydration
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 13. Update Water Log (replace {{log_id}} with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/{{log_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "amount_ml": 300,
  "notes": "Updated amount"
}

### 14. Delete Water Log (replace {{log_id}} with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/water-logs/{{log_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
